it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.analyzer

Class ProtocolAnalyzer

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.analyzer.ProtocolAnalyzer

  • public class ProtocolAnalyzer
extends java.lang.Object
    Protocol analyzer. It provides static methods for inspecting packets. It recursively analyzes packet header and payload of all inner packets.
